 swap rates) from for a wide range of maturities since 2009.
 Bank Of England publishes OIS discount rates from 1 month up to to 5 years
 (every month in between).
 Liquidity in OIS contracts beyond 5 years is limited; therefore BOE only
 publishes OIS curve up to 5 years.
 OIS curves over 5 years generally use OIS spread over LIBOR.
