\begin_layout Enumerate
Price each caplet using the LIBOR rates (Definition 27)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Calculate the cap price as the sum of the caplet prices (Definition 28)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Store the cap price
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Once all simulations are completed, obtain the cap price by averaging the
 cap price obtained for each simulation (expectation)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Compute the implied volatility for the cap using Black76 
\end_layout

