 six months).
 Liquidity in OIS contracts beyond 5 years is limited; therefore BOE only
 publishes OIS curve up to 5 years.
 Minimum data clean-up (exclude public holidays) was required as the data
 has already been cleansed by Bank of England.
 
\end_layout

